TMT Additional Channels:
Genotype:
WT (wild type, no gene knockout);
ATG5 KO (ATG5 gene knockout);
RB1CC1 KO (RB1CC1 gene knockout).

Condition (applied per genotype):
UT = untreated control;
−AA = amino acid withdrawal;
Torin1 = mTOR inhibition.

Modifications:
Fixed: Carbamidomethyl (C);
Variable: Oxidation (M); Acetyl (Protein N-term); 
TMTpro on N-termini and Lysine
